<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent3cd090a510c04ad19f69d14724ce4e9b">
</div>
<p><strong></strong>Cheltenham General Hospital provides general hospital services. </p>
<p>Cheltenham has state-of-the-art critical care facilities and is home to the specialist Oncology Centre as well as breast screening facilities at the Thirlestaine Road clinic. This thriving hospital also has a new Interventional Radiology operating theatre, surgical robot used in treating prostate cancer and provides a wide range of outpatient services.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
